" https://neovim.io/doc/user/nvim_terminal_emulator.html

" Go back to normal mode
tnoremap <ESC> <C-\><C-n>

" Retaining movements
" up, left, down, right
tnoremap <A-c> <C-\><C-n><C-w><C-k>
tnoremap <A-h> <C-\><C-n><C-w><C-h>
tnoremap <A-t> <C-\><C-n><C-w><C-j>
tnoremap <A-n> <C-\><C-n><C-w><C-l>
